{"tid":1524871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然之前圍咁多次狗屋都唔驚 不如新開黨鐵戰線","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:27:49.000Z","uid":31369,"like":72,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f37edebf59f1864d10f588e8b339ad2e981332d3","tid":1524871,"uid":31369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"之前打過咁多次狗屋陣地都輸到仆街<br />\n不過快閃黨鐵 逐個逐個站同佢拆曬啲機 閘同CCTV<br />\n橫掂都封站 咁不如攬炒啦<br />\n個個站都壞曬 <br />\n一係你日日都唔通車 大家罷工<br />\n一係你就照通車 大家免費搭車<br />\n次次去圍黨鐵 屌啲前線職員都冇用<br />\n啲高層理撚得你<br />\n<br />\n拆黨鐵<br />\n一 可以快閃 拆完就走 唔會有陣地 戀戰<br />\n二 起碼唔洗比狗追住黎打 開槍<br />\n三 刑罰無用重 都係刑事毁壞？ 呢層唔清楚 但一定好過暴動<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"6ed4c90b1e9a3be0dfb428cf9f91542c04db6930","tid":1524871,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=7a60725e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=136027f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e460ca37\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"1f9a246903a574a01a1d1fc68dc62f11c0c995e6","tid":1524871,"uid":31369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy